name: Cybermore
description:
Cybermore is a game that will annoy the beans out of you.

You are a nerd trapped in a dungeon that needs to get to the computer to move to the next room.

This game was created with realism in mind so if you die you go back to the start.

Have fun...

If you finish the game (reach room 15) comment below for a cookie.

If you want more levels comment below.

You can download and use the art I made for this game for free here: https://alexhawking.itch.io/cybermore-art-assets
